title: Lava Bucket
author: hotdogs69
pages:
#- This lava bucket was used to grief the city of Megaton at the beginning of 2.0.

Megaton was griefed by hotdogs69 (ServerError404) and whosnick. All reperations since have been paid for the crimes that took place. 

#- Hotdog69's insignia was placing a sign saying "You've been hotdog'd" at the location of his grief.

This piece was donated to Sanwi by ServerError404's private collection on 10/8/14.
